#: ../../../source/docs/getting_started/FAQ.rst:321
msgid ""
"The ``main()`` function is called after startup is complete as a signal that "
"it is safe to call any compiled method."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../source/docs/getting_started/FAQ.rst:324
